{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"iu6nr9qel896bjhbckfl05d","title":"How To Archive and Replay","desc":"","updated":1650937352011,"created":1648539827519,"custom":{},"fname":"howto","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"b0f13edb73ce52dca7e8f70339530b0d","links":[{"from":{"fname":"root","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":201,"offset":1031},"end":{"line":16,"column":223,"offset":1053},"indent":[]},"value":"howto","alias":"contribute"}],"anchors":{"archive-single-pages":{"type":"header","text":"Archive single pages","value":"archive-single-pages","line":9,"column":0,"depth":2},"archive-the-whole-site":{"type":"header","text":"Archive the whole site","value":"archive-the-whole-site","line":15,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["9jou94aipjmxrwmd28tly5u"],"parent":"pfy4h1nwep9age7eg0u8xe1","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"how-to-archive-and-replay\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#how-to-archive-and-replay\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>How To Archive and Replay</h1>\n<h2 id=\"archive-single-pages\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#archive-single-pages\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Archive single pages</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Internet Archive (<a href=\"https://archive.org/web/\">https://archive.org/web/</a>)\n<ul>\n<li>We strongly suggest your installing <a href=\"https://github.com/internetarchive/wayback-machine-webextension\">the Internet Archive plugin for browsers</a> to save any web pages handily. </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Webrecorder Archive (<a href=\"https://webrecorder.net/tools#archivewebpage\">https://webrecorder.net/tools#archivewebpage</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"archive-the-whole-site\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#archive-the-whole-site\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Archive the whole site</h2>\n<p>If you are a developer, you can run up this docker container(<a href=\"https://github.com/webrecorder/browsertrix-crawler\">https://github.com/webrecorder/browsertrix-crawler</a>) to save a web site as a whole. The saved site will be compressed into a single file as a snapshot from the specific date(time). The file is in a popular compression format called <a href=\"https://webrecorder.github.io/wacz-spec/1.1.1/\">WACZ</a>. </p>\n<hr>\n<strong>Children</strong>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/9jou94aipjmxrwmd28tly5u\">Replay the archived files</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/pfy4h1nwep9age7eg0u8xe1\">SHKO(Save Hong Kong Online)</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"pfy4h1nwep9age7eg0u8xe1","title":"SHKO(Save Hong Kong Online)","desc":"","updated":1650946407329,"created":1648525691085,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"2b86c1076b19a68a88243e5002a6b2cb","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"pfy4h1nwep9age7eg0u8xe1","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"background","alias":"the vast disappearing of civil society and independent media","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":129,"offset":346},"end":{"line":5,"column":206,"offset":423},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"background"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"pfy4h1nwep9age7eg0u8xe1","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"sites","alias":"websites or online causes","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":34,"offset":864},"end":{"line":16,"column":71,"offset":901},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"sites"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"pfy4h1nwep9age7eg0u8xe1","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"howto","alias":"contribute","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":201,"offset":1031},"end":{"line":16,"column":223,"offset":1053},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"